Quest: Chapter 1 Day 1


Explain what the Blockchain is in your own words. You can read this to help you, but you don't have to: https://www.investopedia.com/terms/b/blockchain.asp

The blockchain is a special form of database that keeps a record of information in the form of blocks.

Explain what a Smart Contract is. You can read this to help you, but you don't have to: 

A smart contract is a form of initiator for the blockchain that can start a specific process such as a transfer that people can interact with if a specific requirements are met.

Explain the difference between a script and a transaction

A script are a way to view the blockchain data in an read only format because it can not change it and it is free, but on the other hand a transaction is not free and can change data on the blockchain and is the only way to change it.





